<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.6">
<l>kāva laṉilaṅ kaikkiṟai kalaṅ kacca ramcela vuyttumaṟ ṟavaṉ</l>
<l>ēva lamtavirt tāṉeṉṉai yāḷuṭai yempirāṉ,</l>
<l>nāva lampuvi maṉṉarvan tuva ṇaṅka māluṟai kiṉṟatiṅ keṉa</l>
<l>tēvar vantiṟaiñ cuntiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The protector, the one who foiled the force of the other one’s arrows,</l>
<l>Discharging arrows so they went to torment Laṅkā’s king,</l>
<l rend="indent">our lord who possesses me,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr where gods come [and] bow low, as they say,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Māl’s dwelling is here!”</l>
<l>While kings of the fine land of the jambo fruit come [and] worship.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
